== Flock-IRC ==
* Automatic refresh of channel activity
* User Participation (Basic IRC Proxy)
* Associate Avatars with Nicknames
* Capture other IRC events (i.e Topic Change)
* Better Pagination
* Display Member messages by channel
* Conversation Isolation

== Flock-SHOUT ==
* User login
* User can post messages

